        <!-- Description of the service -->
        <p class="card-text">Introducing our comprehensive Game Programming and Design Project Services! Are you looking to turn your gaming idea into reality? Our expert team of developers and designers is here to bring your vision to life. From concept to final release, we offer a full suite of services including game design, programming, 2D/3D art creation, sound design, and quality assurance. With years of industry experience, we ensure your game not only looks stunning but also runs smoothly across platforms. Whether you're an indie developer or a gaming studio, our customized solutions cater to your unique needs. Get ready to level up your game development journey with our top-notch services. Contact us today to embark on your gaming adventure!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Second service card for Web Development -->
  <div class="col">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <!-- Display an image related to Web Development -->
      <img src="img/service2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="web_development">
