        <!-- Title for the service -->
        <h5 class="card-title">Database management</h5>
        <!-- Description of the service -->
        <p class="card-text">Efficiently organizing and managing data is crucial for any business. With expertise in database management systems like MySQL, Oracle, and MongoDB, I can design and optimize databases to ensure data integrity, security, and performance. Whether it's developing efficient queries, establishing data relationships, or implementing data backup strategies, I can help you streamline your data management processes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Fourth service card for Project Management -->
  <div class="col">
    <div class="card h-100">
